AGI -&nbsp; eleven arrests for robbery, extortion, kidnapping in person for extortion, money laundering, drug dealing were performed in the provinces of Rome, Viterbo and Frosinone. The blitz the carabinieri of the Investment Nucleus of the Provincial Command of Rome and the agents of the State Police of the I District Trevi Campo Marzio have given execution to the order of precautionary custody arranged by the gip on request of the District Antimafia> of the prosecutor of Rome.
<br The investigation activity, born in October 2022, originates from the complaints of a drug consumer who had matured with the drug dealers a debt that had no longer been able to honor, generating the violent reactions of the latter. In particular, the investigation activity, which lasted over a year, has allowed to collect serious evidence of guilt > regarding the existence of a criminal group, operating in the Roman district of Cinecittà, of which the investigated and to document how the latter were used to operate violent retaliation with regard to the buyers of morbid drugs.
<br> Proportionary elements were collected, so in some episodes the victims were transported into the houses of certain subsidiaries where they were lost and threatened with a gun pointed at the temple in order to force them to make payments, even through bank transfers. Sometimes, since the daily "plafond" had been exhausted at the bank, they were seized and malmented all night, waiting to make other transfers the next morning. In cases where they couldn't get the money claimed, threats were also extended to the family of the sick. The analysis of the flow of money extorted > (more than 300 thousand euros) has allowed to identify all beneficiaries of bank transfers in subjects considered close to the most authoritative subject of the criminal group, Daniele Salvatori and to document the activities aimed at re-use and money laundering that from the various current accounts came, through additional transfers or through the cash withdrawal, transferred to other beneficiaries.
&nbsp;
In Salvatori, 47 years old, already known to the law enforcement forces, on 12 June 2023, the military of the Investigative Nucleus of Rome had already notified a stop of suspected crime, issued by the Dda, for the extortion to the damage of a 36-year-old resident in the province of Frosinone >e of his family. On 3 October 2022, Salvatori had been arrested in scourgency of crime by the military of the Cassino Radiomobile Section (FR), as he was surprised near the home of the victims in possession of a clandestine weapon.&nbsp;

